{"tid":429382,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"屈福特新星叫雞時不舉求回水被捕","createTime":"2017-10-09T00:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T01:20:10.000Z","uid":31314,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e7508717de5cd530c42b7220e57c8d235cf48f75","tid":429382,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T00:11:46.000Z","msg":"屈福特新星艾錫瑟薩斯未紅先驕，日前被踢爆涉嫌食「霸王餐」，遭到英國警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n年僅21歲的尼日利亞快馬艾錫瑟薩斯（Isaac Success）去年加盟屈福特，上季英超披甲17場，周薪3萬鎊，日前被英國《太陽報》揭發醜聞。據知，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>瑟薩斯早前前往酒店向4名性工作者支付2000鎊肉金，但因興奮過度，喝了2支愛爾蘭威士忌，導致性功能失調，由始至終也沒跟其中一人進行性交易。 因此，瑟薩斯決定惡人先告狀，爭取拿回2000鎊肉金，雙方爭持不下，最後警方到場，把前者拘捕</strong></span>，其中一名性工作者Alexis Domerge受訪時大爆細節。 「90分鐘時間，他吹噓自己的性能力很強，向我們每人付了500鎊，但他已無法勃起，於是要求拿回金錢。」Domerge不屑表示。<br />\n<br />\n2&amp;b既同鄉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458f1d9f914de2e9f60e12ac9de7e8eda4bd0c33","tid":429382,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T00:25:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">2&amp;b</span>既同鄉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n重點變左25b <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b6dad29221ba02675c24cc3e7d051291eecdc1","tid":429382,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T00:25:54.000Z","msg":"同佢唔熟..."},{"pid":"23c942103fa469a4d3eb904ecae412497b5277c3","tid":429382,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T00:38:53.000Z","msg":"90分鐘，他吹噓自己射門能力很強.........<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed24a607ac1de7e1394bc685858d8be8ac3be92","tid":429382,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T01:00:49.000Z","msg":"一J難敵4對波"},{"pid":"d9732cf35641c29dae9574def1124e738d3053ec","tid":429382,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T01:02:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}